reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Travel Essentials Perfected with Depoza's 16-Pack Bottles Set
reviews.reviewText: he Depoza 16 Pack Travel Bottles Set is a game-changer for anyone who values convenience, organization, and compliance with TSA regulations. This meticulously crafted set of leak-proof silicone squeezable containers has become an essential companion for my travels, and here's why.First and foremost, the TSA-approved design ensures a hassle-free experience at airport security checkpoints. The bottles meet the size requirements for carry-on liquids, allowing you to breeze through without the stress of confiscation. The clear, quart-sized toiletry bag provided adds an extra layer of organization, making it easy to locate your essentials.Leakage is a common concern with travel-sized bottles, but Depoza has conquered this issue with their innovative design. The silicone material not only makes the bottles squeezable for effortless dispensing but also guarantees a tight seal. I've experienced zero leaks, even when the bottles were subjected to various movements and changes in air pressure.The set offers a variety of bottle sizes and types to accommodate different toiletries. From shampoo and conditioner to lotion and facial cleanser, each bottle serves its purpose efficiently. The wide openings make refilling a breeze, and the labels included help distinguish the contents of each bottle – a thoughtful touch for those who like to stay organized.The durability of the silicone material ensures that these bottles can withstand the rigors of travel. They're flexible enough to squeeze out every last drop of product, and the translucent design allows you to monitor the remaining amount easily. The sturdy caps and well-designed spouts further contribute to the overall reliability of the set.Beyond air travel, these travel bottles have proven handy for camping trips, gym sessions, or simply keeping your favorite products on hand in your everyday bag. The versatility of the Depoza 16 Pack extends beyond travel, making it a practical investment for various occasions.In conclusion, the Depoza 16 Pack Travel Bottles Set has truly perfected the art of travel-sized toiletry containers. With a focus on TSA compliance, leak-proof design, and overall convenience, this set has become an integral part of my travel routine. Say goodbye to spills and fumbling through security – elevate your travel experience with these reliable and well-crafted travel bottles.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect assortment of travel containers
reviews.reviewText: Was happy to find a kit that had two larger containers for shampoo and conditioner, which I use the most, and smaller ones for just the right amount of other things. Plus really appreciated the two spray bottles, smaller than the usual travel bottles and perfect for hair spray or body mist. So far the small tubs are proving leakproof, at least for the foundation and hand cream I put in them. The tiny spoons and brush nice touches for filling/emptying and cleaning. Also love how soft the containers are, very easy to squeeze contents out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A convenient and useful product!
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this for a recent international trip I went on. The product worked great, no spillage or leaking in my full suitcase. The stickers they provided were useful for labeling my shampoo, conditioner, etc. I also liked the design of the bottles and the variety of shapes/types and sizes— for example, I put leave in conditioner in the spray bottle and face lotion in the smaller round containers. The clear bag was also nice to see everything that I had packed. Very solid and reliable product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great set, bright colors, small containers are not super leak proof
reviews.reviewText: This is a nice travel set and I like the spray container. It's also easy to clean each of these. My only issue is that the smallest containers leak occasionally.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a great set of travel containers. Comes with labels, scrapers, funnel & cleaning brush. So many sizes for liquids & solids. The silicone is so soft & flexible! Sizes are TSA approved & all in a handy bag.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for carry-on & staying within regulations
reviews.reviewText: Great little set. I used it for mouthwash, facial cleanser, toner, and two facial creams as well as shower soap, shampoo, and conditioner. It was perfect. It comes with little scoopers to transfer your creams into the little jars. It made my life easier having this set to accommodate my personal care products.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for travel
reviews.reviewText: Set is good. Didn't try the spray bottle, but the other ones kept everything in. Only problem I had was with the tiny short transparent ones. Ok for creamy stuff, but not liquids. Had my liquid nitrogena and it kept leaking out during my travel making everything in the pouch a mess, no matter how much I tighten it up.Otherwise, the bigger ones contained more than I expected. Was away for over a week and came back with some bottles still half full.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My first trip with these to Hawaii and no leaking! The bag fits perfectly in my new toiletry bag and no leaking for me. I also didn’t super fill them up either. I did use shampoo, conditioner, lotion, and facial cleanser. And in the small little pill boxes I put eye serum, face moisturizer and foundation make-up. In the spray bottle I put some Burke Williams essential oil shower spray so we can enjoy it on our trip. So glad these didn’t leak. And very thankful for the little spatulas and the cleaning brush and labels!
